{"cf_tracking_thunderbird_esr52": "---", "status": "RESOLVED", "cf_tracking_firefox60": "---", "attachments": [{"creator": "xidorn+moz@upsuper.org", "is_obsolete": 0, "is_patch": 0, "flags": [], "content_type": "image/png", "id": 8532569}], "classification": "Components", "creator": "xidorn+moz@upsuper.org", "cc": ["jfkthame@gmail.com", "siqinbilige@gmail.com", "xidorn+moz@upsuper.org"], "depends_on": [], "creation_time": "2014-12-05T17:59:01Z", "cf_user_story": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_relnote": "---", "platform": "x86_64", "cf_status_firefox58": "---", "cf_status_firefox59": "---", "keywords": [], "summary": "Line box boundaries is incorrect for vertical text", "id": 1107960, "assigned_to_detail": {"email": "nobody@mozilla.org", "id": 1, "name": "nobody@mozilla.org", "real_name": "Nobody; OK to take it and work on it"}, "severity": "normal", "is_confirmed": true, "is_creator_accessible": true, "cf_has_regression_range": "---", "assigned_to": "nobody@mozilla.org", "comment_count": 6, "comments": [{"text": "Created attachment 8532569\nline-box.png\n\nSee the attachment, the line box and the text do not match.", "author": "xidorn+moz@upsuper.org", "id": 9664061, "time": "2014-12-05T17:59:01Z"}, {"text": "Is it same as https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1095334 ?", "author": "siqinbilige@gmail.com", "id": 9665728, "time": "2014-12-06T03:36:02Z"}, {"text": "(In reply to siqinbilige from comment #1)\n> Is it same as https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1095334 ?\n\nProbably, but I won't actually mark as a duplicate until we've investigated a bit to confirm this.", "author": "jfkthame@gmail.com", "id": 9665806, "time": "2014-12-06T07:31:42Z"}, {"text": "I don't think they are the same problem. Bug 1095334 is a problem about the selection area, which I guess should have been fixed. At least, I don't think we see that problem today. However, this bug is about painting border and possibly also background rect, not the selection area.", "author": "xidorn+moz@upsuper.org", "id": 9665810, "time": "2014-12-06T07:37:20Z"}, {"text": "I think this may have been fixed by various font-metrics patches that have landed recently; could you please confirm whether you're still seeing this issue? Thanks.", "author": "jfkthame@gmail.com", "id": 9812191, "time": "2015-01-19T13:14:14Z"}, {"text": "It seems the boundaries have been correct.\n\nAnother problem is that the block size of inline elements seems to be a little too wide. I guess you probably have known this problem. If not, I can submit a bug for it.", "author": "xidorn+moz@upsuper.org", "id": 9814452, "time": "2015-01-19T22:38:24Z"}], "cf_last_resolved": "2015-01-19T22:38:24Z", "priority": "--", "mentors_detail": [], "cf_crash_signature": "", "version": "Trunk", "cf_qa_whiteboard": "", "cf_tracking_firefox_esr52": "---", "cf_tracking_firefox59": "---", "last_change_time": "2015-01-19T22:38:24Z", "cf_platform_rel": "---", "product": "Core", "cf_status_firefox_esr52": "---", "blocks": [1099032], "qa_contact": "", "see_also": [], "cf_fx_iteration": "---", "component": "Layout", "votes": 0, "groups": [], "cf_status_firefox60": "---", "target_milestone": "---", "is_cc_accessible": true, "cf_status_thunderbird_esr52": "---", "url": "", "creator_detail": {"email": "xidorn+moz@upsuper.org", "id": 373403, "name": "xidorn+moz@upsuper.org", "real_name": "Xidorn Quan [:xidorn] UTC+10"}, "whiteboard": "", "mentors": [], "cc_detail": [{"email": "jfkthame@gmail.com", "id": 329583, "name": "jfkthame@gmail.com", "real_name": "Jonathan Kew (:jfkthame) [PTO, 5-16 Mar]"}, {"email": "siqinbilige@gmail.com", "id": 512533, "name": "siqinbilige@gmail.com", "real_name": ""}, {"email": "xidorn+moz@upsuper.org", "id": 373403, "name": "xidorn+moz@upsuper.org", "real_name": "Xidorn Quan [:xidorn] UTC+10"}], "cf_has_str": "---", "alias": null, "dupe_of": null, "flags": [], "cf_tracking_firefox58": "---", "cf_rank": null, "is_open": false, "history": [{"changes": [{"removed": "", "field_name": "blocks", "